expression.expression:
SELECT 
st.[STUDY_ID],
st.STUDY_CREATION_DATE,
t1.id as [SIGNAL_ID],
t1.original_snapshot as [ORIGINAL_SNAPSHOT_ID], 
t1.created as SIGNAL_CREATION_DATE,
t1.[CURRENT_STATE_NAME] as [CURRENT_STATE_NAME],

/*recode current state name to reflect new signal mitigation process*/
CASE 
WHEN t1.[current_state_name] IN ('open', 'watch', 'alert') THEN 'Open'
WHEN t1.[current_state_name] IN ('closed', 'standby') THEN 'Closed'
WHEN t1.[current_state_name] like 'new' then 'New'
WHEN t1.[current_state_name] like 'in_review' THEN 'In Review'
WHEN t1.[current_state_name] like 'draft' THEN 'Draft'
END as CURRENT_STATE_V1,
CASE 
WHEN t1.[priority] IS NOT NULL then t1.[priority]
WHEN t1.[current_state_name]='alert' THEN 'High'
END as CURRENT_PRIORITY_V1,

CASE WHEN 
sig_h.[ALERT_IN_HISTORY]=1 OR t1.[CURRENT_STATE_NAME]='alert' then 1
ELSE 0
END as ALERT_IN_HISTORY,
CASE WHEN 
sig_h.[WATCH_IN_HISTORY]=1 OR t1.[CURRENT_STATE_NAME]='watch' then 1
ELSE 0
END as WATCH_IN_HISTORY,
CASE WHEN 
sig_h.[STANDBY_IN_HISTORY]=1 OR t1.[CURRENT_STATE_NAME]='standby' then 1
ELSE 0
END as STANDBY_IN_HISTORY,
CASE WHEN 
sig_h.[CLOSED_IN_HISTORY]=1 OR t1.[CURRENT_STATE_NAME]='closed' then 1
ELSE 0
END as CLOSED_IN_HISTORY,
ext_date.[EXTRACTION_DATE],


CASE WHEN 
sig_h.[OPEN_IN_HISTORY_V1]=1 OR t1.[current_state_name] IN ('open', 'watch', 'alert') THEN 1
ELSE 0
END as OPEN_IN_HISTORY_V1,
CASE WHEN 
sig_h.[CLOSED_IN_HISTORY_V1]=1 OR t1.[current_state_name] IN ('closed','standby') THEN 1
ELSE 0
END as CLOSED_IN_HISTORY_V1,
CASE WHEN 
sig_h.[HIGH_IN_HISTORY_V1]=1 OR t1.[current_state_name] = 'alert' OR t1.[priority]='High' THEN 1
ELSE 0
END as HIGH_IN_HISTORY_V1,
CASE WHEN 
sig_h.[MEDIUM_IN_HISTORY_V1]=1 OR t1.[priority]='Medium' THEN 1
ELSE 0
END as MEDIUM_IN_HISTORY_V1,
CASE WHEN
sig_h.[LOW_IN_HISTORY_V1]=1 OR t1.[priority]='Low' THEN 1
ELSE 0
END as LOW_IN_HISTORY_V1,

CASE
WHEN t1.[CURRENT_STATE_NAME]='new' then daydiff(ext_date.[EXTRACTION_DATE], t1.[current_state_creation])
END as DIFFDAY_NEW_CURRENT,
CASE
WHEN t1.[CURRENT_STATE_NAME]='watch' then daydiff(ext_date.[EXTRACTION_DATE], t1.[current_state_creation])
END as DIFFDAY_WATCH_CURRENT,
CASE
WHEN t1.[CURRENT_STATE_NAME]='alert' then daydiff(ext_date.[EXTRACTION_DATE], t1.[current_state_creation])
END as DIFFDAY_ALERT_CURRENT,

CASE 
WHEN t1.[current_state_rationale] not like 'This status was migrated by automated process during the 2.11.0 release.'  THEN daydiff(ext_date.[EXTRACTION_DATE], t1.[current_state_creation]) 
ELSE daydiff(ext_date.[EXTRACTION_DATE], ssh1.[created])
END as DIFFDAY_SIG_CURRENT_EXTRACT,

CASE
WHEN t1.[current_state_rationale] like 'This status was migrated by automated process during the 2.11.0 release.'  THEN ssh1.[created]
ELSE t1.[current_state_creation]
END as CURRENT_DATETIME,
CASE
WHEN t1.[current_state_rationale] like 'This status was migrated by automated process during the 2.11.0 release.'  THEN ssh1.[rationale]
ELSE t1.[current_state_rationale]
END as CURRENT_STATE_RATIONALE, 
ssh1.[name] as PREVIOUS_STATE,
ssh1.[created] as PREVIOUS_STATE_DATE,
ssh1.[rationale] as PREVIOUS_RATIONALE


FROM SIGNAL as t1

LEFT JOIN SIGNAL_HISTORY_DERIV as sig_h
ON sig_h.[SIGNAL_ID] = t1.[id]
LEFT JOIN FACTS_STUDY_DERIV as st
on st.[STUDY_ID] = t1.[STUDY]
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT MAX(ID) as max_id, signal
FROM SIGNAL_STATE_HISTORY
GROUP BY signal) as ssh
on ssh.[signal]=t1.[id]
LEFT JOIN SIGNAL_STATE_HISTORY as ssh1
on ssh.[signal]=ssh1.[signal] AND ssh.[max_id]=ssh1.[ID]
CROSS JOIN DIM_EXTRACTION_DATE as ext_date

WHERE st.[STUDY_ID] IS NOT NULL

SELECT 
t1.id as ACTION_ID,
t2.GROUPING_TYPE, 
CASE
WHEN t1.status like 'new' Then 'New'
WHEN t1.status like 'open' Then 'Open'
WHEN t1.status like 'resolved' Then 'Resolved'
WHEN t1.status like 'rejected' Then 'Rejected'
WHEN t1.status like 'deprecated' Then 'Deprecated'
WHEN t1.status like 'stalled' Then 'Stalled'
END as STATUS,
CASE 
WHEN t1.[status] in ('new', 'open', 'stalled') then 1
ELSE 0
END as ACTIONS_STATUS_ACTIVE,
t3.name as CATEGORY, 
t1.code as CODE,
t1.title as TITLE,
t1.[desc] as DESCRIPTION,
t1.ctms_action as [CTMS_ACTION],
t4.[ACTION_CREATION_DATE],
t1.[updated] as CURRENT_ACTION_DATE,
t4.[DUE_DATE_AVAILABLE],
t1.[due] as DUE_DATE

FROM ACTION as t1
LEFT JOIN DIM_SIGNAL as t2
on t1.[signal]=t2.[SIGNAL_ID]
LEFT JOIN ACTION_CATEGORY as t3
on t1.[category]=t3.[id]
LEFT JOIN FACTS_ACTION_DERIV as t4
on t1.[id]=t4.[ACTION_ID]

WHERE t2.[SIGNAL_ID] IS NOT NULL

SELECT
t1.[id] as [SIGNAL_ID], 
t2.[name] as CATEGORY, 
t1.[code] as CODE, 
t1.[name] as TITLE,
t1.[description] as DESCRIPTION,
t1.[name] as NAME,
t1.[created] as SIGNAL_CREATION_DATE,
t4.[CURRENT_DATETIME],
t1.[original_snapshot] as ORIGINAL_SNAPSHOT_ID, 
CASE 
WHEN t1.[grouping_type_category] ='center' then 'Center'
WHEN t1.[grouping_type_category] ='region' then 'Region'
WHEN t1.[grouping_type_category] ='subject' then 'Patient'
WHEN t1.[grouping_type_category] IS NULL then 'Non-Assigned'
END as GROUPING_TYPE,
CASE 
WHEN t4.[current_state_name] like 'in_review' THEN 'In Review'
WHEN t4.[current_state_name] like 'draft' THEN 'Draft'
WHEN t4.[current_state_name] like 'new' THEN 'New'
WHEN t4.[current_state_name] like 'standby' THEN 'Standby'
WHEN t4.[current_state_name] like 'watch' THEN 'Watch'
WHEN t4.[current_state_name] like 'alert' THEN 'Alert'
WHEN t4.[current_state_name] like 'closed' THEN 'Closed'
WHEN t4.[current_state_name] like 'open' THEN 'Open'
END as CURRENT_STATE,
t4.[CURRENT_STATE_V1],
t4.[CURRENT_PRIORITY_V1],
CASE
WHEN t4.[current_state_name] IN ('draft', 'in_review') then 'Draft/In Review'
WHEN t4.[current_state_name] IN ('new') then 'New'
ELSE 'Mitigated'
END as MITIGATION, 

t4.[current_state_rationale] as CURRENT_STATE_RATIONALE, 
t3.[visualization] as VISUALIZATION,
CASE WHEN t3.[visualization] IN ('bubble_extreme', 'dashboard_patients', 'extreme') then 'DQA'
WHEN t3.[visualization]='KRI' then 'KRI'
WHEN t3.[visualization] IS NULL then 'Non Assigned'
END as VISUALIZATION_RECODED,
t1.location as LOCATION,
t4.[ALERT_IN_HISTORY],
t4.[CLOSED_IN_HISTORY],
t4.[STANDBY_IN_HISTORY],
t4.[WATCH_IN_HISTORY],
t4.[OPEN_IN_HISTORY_V1],
t4.[CLOSED_IN_HISTORY_V1],
t4.[HIGH_IN_HISTORY_V1],
t4.[MEDIUM_IN_HISTORY_V1], 
t4.[LOW_IN_HISTORY_V1],
t6.[CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE],
t6.[CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_RATIONALE],
t6.[CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_DATE],
t6.[CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_RATIONALE_DATE],
CASE WHEN t7.[SIGNAL_ID] is null THEN 0
ELSE 1
END as ACTION_NEW_OPEN_STALLED

FROM [SIGNAL] as t1
LEFT JOIN [SIGNAL_CATEGORY] as t2
on t1.[category]=t2.[id]
LEFT JOIN [ANALYSIS] as t3
on t1.[analysis]=t3.[id]
LEFT JOIN [FACTS_SIGNAL_DERIV] as t4
on t1.[id]=t4.[SIGNAL_ID]
LEFT JOIN [DIM_STUDY] as t5
on t1.[study]=t5.[STUDY_ID]
LEFT JOIN [DIM_SIGNAL_ROOT_CAUSE_DERIV] as t6
on t1.[id]=t6.[SIGNAL_ID]
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT DISTINCT SIGNAL_ID
FROM FACTS_ACTION_DERIV
WHERE ACTION_CURRENT_STATUS IN ('new','open', 'stalled')) as t7
on t1.[id]=t7.[SIGNAL_ID]
WHERE t5.[STUDY_ID] IS NOT NULL
SELECT DISTINCT DATETIME_TYPE FROM FACTS_STUDY_SIGNAL_ACTION

SELECT MIN(start_time) as EXTRACTION_DATE
FROM extraction_log

SELECT 
t1.id as KRI_DEFINITION_ID,
t2.[ANALYSIS_ID],
t2.[SNAPSHOT_ID],
t3.[study] as STUDY_ID,
tostring(t3.[study])+'_'+tostring([CODE]) as STUDY_ID_CODE,
t1.[expected] as EXPECTED,
t1.[value_thresholds_above_high] as VALUE_THRESHOLDS_ABOVE_HIGH,
t1.[value_thresholds_above_medium] as VALUE_THRESHOLDS_ABOVE_MEDIUM,
t1.[value_thresholds_below_high] as VALUE_THRESHOLDS_BELOW_HIGH,
t1.[value_thresholds_below_medium] as VALUE_THRESHOLDS_BELOW_MEDIUM
FROM [KRI] as t1
LEFT JOIN [DIM_ANALYSIS_KRI] as t2
ON t1.[ANALYSIS]=t2.[ANALYSIS_ID]
LEFT JOIN SNAPSHOT as t3
ON t2.[SNAPSHOT_ID]=t3.[ID]
LEFT JOIN [STUDY] as t4
on t3.[study]=t4.[id]
WHERE upper(t4.[name]) not like '%TRN%'

SELECT DISTINCT DATETIME as DATE from FACTS_STUDY_SIGNAL_ACTION 
UNION
SELECT CREATEDATE(1900,01,01)

SELECT 
t1.id as [STUDY_ID], 
t1.name as [NAME], 
t1.alias as [ALIAS], 
t1.description as [DESCRIPTION],
t1.therapeutic_area as [THERAPEUTIC_AREA], 
t1.asset_type as [ASSET_TYPE], 
t1.phase as [PHASE], 
t1.indication as [INDICATION], 
t1.created as STUDY_CREATION_DATE,
CASE WHEN t1.locked=0 then 'Not Locked Study'
WHEN t1.locked=1 then 'Locked Study'
END as LOCKED_DESC,
CASE WHEN t1.indication='Acute Coronary Syndrome' then 'Acute coronary disease' 
WHEN t1.indication='Accute Myelod Leukemia' then 'Acute Myeloid Leukemia'
WHEN t1.indication='Allergic Rhinits' then 'Allergic Rhinitis'
WHEN t1.indication like 'Alzheimer%' then 'Alzheimers Disease'
WHEN t1.indication='Dermatitis atopic' then 'Dermatitis (atopic dermatitis)'
WHEN t1.indication='Duchenne Muscular dystrophy' then 'Duchenne Muscular Dystrophy'
WHEN t1.indication='Glabellar Lines' then 'Glabellar lines (GL)'
WHEN t1.indication='Myelodysplastic syndromes' then 'Myelodysplastic Syndrome'
WHEN t1.indication='Neoplasm,Non-small cell lung cancer' then 'Neoplasm, Non-small cell lung cancer'
WHEN t1.indication='Not applicable' then 'Not Applicable'
WHEN t1.indication in ('Pneumococcal Infections', 'Pneumococcal infection', 'Pneumococcal Disease') then 'Pneumococcal Infection'
WHEN t1.indication='Ulcerative Colitis' then 'Ulcerative Colitis (UC)'
ELSE t1.indication
END as INDICATION_RECODED,
CASE WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Cardiovascular', 'Transcatheter Aortic Heart Valve') then 'Cardiovascular and metabolic diseases'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Cerebrovascular Diseases', 'Central Nervous System (CNS)', 'MS Neurology Ophthalmology Dev', 'Neurology/Psychiatry', 'Neurology') then 'Neurology/Central Nervous System (CNS)'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA LIKE ('%GI%') then 'Gastroenterology'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Immunology') then 'Immunology/Rheumatology'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Atypical Hemolytic Uremic Syndrome (aHUS)', 'Diabetic Kidney Disease', 'Rare Disease/ Nephrology', 'Urology', 'Nephrology') then 'Nephrology/Urology'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Dermatology', 'Medical Aesthetics and Derm') then 'Medical Aesthetics/Dermatology'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Metabolic Disorders') then 'Metabolic Disease'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Psychiatry and Addiction', 'Psychiatry') then 'Psychiatry/Addiction'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Respiratory disorder') then 'Pulmonary/Respiratory'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Inflammation', 'Pain and Inflammation') then 'Pain/Inflammation'
ELSE t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA
END as THERAPEUTIC_AREA_RECODED


FROM STUDY as t1 
RIGHT JOIN 
(SELECT DISTINCT sn.[STUDY]
FROM ANALYSIS as a
LEFT JOIN SNAPSHOT as sn
on sn.[id]=a.[snapshot]
WHERE a.[visualization] ='KRI') as An
on an.[study]=t1.[id]
WHERE upper(t1.[name]) not like '%TRN%'

SELECT DISTINCT COALESCE (RC.SIGNAL_ID, RCR.SIGNAL_ID) as SIGNAL_ID, RC.CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE, RC.CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_DATE, RCR.CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_RATIONALE, RCR.CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_RATIONALE_DATE

FROM
(SELECT RC_ID.[signal] as SIGNAL_ID, SF2.after as CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE, SF2.created as CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_DATE
FROM (SELECT MAX(SF.[id]) as CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_ID, SF.[signal]
FROM SIGNAL_FIELD_UPDATE AS SF
WHERE SF.[field]='root_cause'
GROUP BY SF.[signal]) as RC_ID
LEFT JOIN SIGNAL_FIELD_UPDATE AS SF2
on RC_ID.CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_ID=SF2.ID) as RC

FULL OUTER JOIN

(SELECT RCR_ID.[signal] as SIGNAL_ID, SF4.after as CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_RATIONALE, SF4.created as CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_RATIONALE_DATE
FROM 
(SELECT MAX(SF3.[id]) as CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_RATIONALE_ID, SF3.[signal]
FROM SIGNAL_FIELD_UPDATE AS SF3
WHERE SF3.[field]='root_cause_rationale'
GROUP BY SF3.[signal]) as RCR_ID
LEFT JOIN SIGNAL_FIELD_UPDATE AS SF4
on RCR_ID.CURRENT_ROOT_CAUSE_RATIONALE_ID=SF4.ID) as RCR
on RC.SIGNAL_ID=RCR.SIGNAL_ID

select id
from study 
where id is null

SELECT 
t1.*,
t2.id as [ACTION_ID], 
t2.status as ACTION_CURRENT_STATUS, 
t2.due as ACTION_DUE_DATE, 
CASE WHEN 
t2.created is null THEN CreateDate(2015,01,01)
ELSE
t2.created
END as [ACTION_CREATION_DATE],
CASE WHEN
t2.[STATUS]='open' and t2.[due] IS NOT NULL THEN daydiff(ext_date.[EXTRACTION_DATE], t2.[DUE]) 
END as DIFFDAY_OPEN_CURRENT,

CASE
WHEN t2.[STATUS]='new' THEN daydiff(ext_date.[EXTRACTION_DATE], t2.[created])
WHEN t2.[status]!='new' THEN daydiff(ext_date.[EXTRACTION_DATE], t4.[created])  
END as DIFFDAY_ACTION_CURRENT_EXTRACT,
CASE
WHEN t2.[due] IS NOT NULL THEN daydiff(ext_date.[EXTRACTION_DATE], t2.[DUE]) 
END as DIFFDAY_ACTION_DUE_CURRENT_EXTRACT,
CASE
WHEN t2.[due] IS NOT NULL THEN 'Due Date Available'
ELSE 'No Due Date'
END as DUE_DATE_AVAILABLE

FROM ACTION as t2
LEFT JOIN 
(SELECT MAX(ID) as max_id, action
FROM ACTION_FIELD_UPDATE
WHERE field='status'
GROUP BY action) as t3
on t2.[id]=t3.[action]
LEFT JOIN ACTION_FIELD_UPDATE as t4
on t3.[max_id]=t4.[id]
LEFT JOIN FACTS_SIGNAL_DERIV as t1 
on t1.[SIGNAL_ID] = t2.[signal]
CROSS JOIN DIM_EXTRACTION_DATE as ext_date

WHERE t1.[SIGNAL_ID] IS NOT NULL

SELECT 
st.[id] as [STUDY_ID],
st.[created] as STUDY_CREATION_DATE,
ext_date.[EXTRACTION_DATE]
FROM STUDY as st
RIGHT JOIN 
(SELECT DISTINCT [STUDY]
FROM SIGNAL) as sig
on sig.[study]=st.[id]
CROSS JOIN DIM_EXTRACTION_DATE as ext_date
WHERE upper(st.[name]) not like '%TRN%'

SELECT 
t1.[id] as ANALYSIS_ID,
t1.created as ANALYSIS_CREATION_DATE,
t1.snapshot as SNAPSHOT_ID,
CASE 
WHEN  t1.grouping_type ='center' then 'Center'
WHEN  t1.grouping_type ='region' then 'Region'
WHEN  t1.grouping_type ='subject' then 'Patient'
END as GROUPING_TYPE
FROM ANALYSIS as t1
LEFT JOIN SNAPSHOT as t2
ON t1.[snapshot]=t2.[ID]
LEFT JOIN DIM_STUDY_KRI as t3
on t2.[study]=t3.[STUDY_ID]

WHERE visualization='KRI' AND t3.[STUDY_ID] IS NOT NULL

SELECT DISTINCT
t1.[id] as STUDY_ID, 
t1.[name] as [NAME], 
t1.[alias] as [ALIAS], 
t1.[description] as [DESCRIPTION],
t1.[therapeutic_area] as [THERAPEUTIC_AREA], 
t1.[asset_type] as [ASSET_TYPE], 
t1.[phase] as [PHASE], 
t1.[indication] as [INDICATION], 
t1.[created] as STUDY_CREATION_DATE,
CASE WHEN locked=0 then 'Not Locked Study'
WHEN locked=1 then 'Locked Study'
END as LOCKED_DESC,
CASE WHEN indication='Acute Coronary Syndrome' then 'Acute coronary disease' 
WHEN indication='Accute Myelod Leukemia' then 'Acute Myeloid Leukemia'
WHEN indication='Allergic Rhinits' then 'Allergic Rhinitis'
WHEN indication like 'Alzheimer%' then 'Alzheimers Disease'
WHEN indication='Dermatitis atopic' then 'Dermatitis (atopic dermatitis)'
WHEN indication='Duchenne Muscular dystrophy' then 'Duchenne Muscular Dystrophy'
WHEN indication='Glabellar Lines' then 'Glabellar lines (GL)'
WHEN indication='Myelodysplastic syndromes' then 'Myelodysplastic Syndrome'
WHEN indication='Neoplasm,Non-small cell lung cancer' then 'Neoplasm, Non-small cell lung cancer'
WHEN indication='Not applicable' then 'Not Applicable'
WHEN indication in ('Pneumococcal Infections', 'Pneumococcal infection', 'Pneumococcal Disease') then 'Pneumococcal Infection'
WHEN indication='Ulcerative Colitis' then 'Ulcerative Colitis (UC)'
ELSE indication
END as INDICATION_RECODED,
CASE WHEN THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Cardiovascular', 'Transcatheter Aortic Heart Valve') then 'Cardiovascular and metabolic diseases'
WHEN THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Cerebrovascular Diseases', 'Central Nervous System (CNS)', 'MS Neurology Ophthalmology Dev', 'Neurology/Psychiatry', 'Neurology') then 'Neurology/Central Nervous System (CNS)'
WHEN THERAPEUTIC_AREA LIKE ('%GI%') then 'Gastroenterology'
WHEN THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Immunology') then 'Immunology/Rheumatology'
WHEN THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Atypical Hemolytic Uremic Syndrome (aHUS)', 'Diabetic Kidney Disease', 'Rare Disease/ Nephrology', 'Urology', 'Nephrology') then 'Nephrology/Urology'
WHEN THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Dermatology', 'Medical Aesthetics and Derm') then 'Medical Aesthetics/Dermatology'
WHEN THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Metabolic Disorders') then 'Metabolic Disease'
WHEN THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Psychiatry and Addiction', 'Psychiatry') then 'Psychiatry/Addiction'
WHEN THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Respiratory disorder') then 'Pulmonary/Respiratory'
WHEN THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Inflammation', 'Pain and Inflammation') then 'Pain/Inflammation'
ELSE THERAPEUTIC_AREA
END as THERAPEUTIC_AREA_RECODED,
CASE WHEN DQA.[STUDY_ID] is null THEN 0
ELSE 1
END as DQA_IN_HISTORY,
CASE WHEN KRI.[STUDY_ID] is null THEN 0
ELSE 1
END as KRI_IN_HISTORY,
CASE WHEN SIGNAL.[STUDY_ID] is null THEN 0
ELSE 1
END as SIGNAL_IN_HISTORY,
CASE WHEN ACTION.[STUDY_ID] is null THEN 0
ELSE 1
END as ACTION_IN_HISTORY,
CASE WHEN DUP.[STUDY_ID] is null THEN 0
ELSE 1
END as DUP_PATIENT_IN_HISTORY,
CASE WHEN RACT.[STUDY_ID] is null THEN 0
ELSE 1
END as RACT_IN_HISTORY

FROM STUDY as t1
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT DISTINCT STUDY_ID
FROM SNAPSHOT_ANALYSIS_DERIV
WHERE [visualization] IN ('bubble_extreme', 'dashboard_patients', 'extreme')) as DQA
on t1.[ID]=DQA.[STUDY_ID]
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT DISTINCT STUDY_ID
FROM SNAPSHOT_ANALYSIS_DERIV
WHERE [visualization] ='KRI') as KRI
on t1.[ID]=KRI.[STUDY_ID]
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT DISTINCT STUDY_ID
FROM SNAPSHOT_ANALYSIS_DERIV
WHERE [visualization] ='duplicate_patients') as DUP
on t1.[ID]=DUP.[STUDY_ID]
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT DISTINCT STUDY_ID
FROM DIM_STUDY_RACT) as RACT
on t1.[ID]=RACT.[STUDY_ID]
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT DISTINCT study as STUDY_ID
FROM SIGNAL
WHERE [current_state_name] IN ('new', 'alert', 'watch', 'closed', 'standby', 'open')) as SIGNAL
on signal.[STUDY_ID]=t1.[id]
LEFT JOIN
(SELECT DISTINCT study as STUDY_ID
FROM SIGNAL as sig
LEFT JOIN ACTION as act
on sig.[id]=act.[signal]
WHERE act.[id] IS NOT NULL) as ACTION
on action.[STUDY_ID]=t1.[id]


WHERE upper(NAME) not like '%TRN%'

SELECT 
STUDY_ID, 
STUDY_CREATION_DATE as DATETIME,
'Study Creation' as DATETIME_TYPE,
NULL as ORIGINAL_SNAPSHOT_ID, 
NULL as SIGNAL_ID,
NULL as ACTION_ID,
NULL as ACTION_CURRENT_STATUS,
CASE WHEN STUDY_ID IS NULL THEN 0
ELSE NULL
END as DIFFDAY_NEW_CURRENT,
CASE WHEN STUDY_ID IS NULL THEN 0
ELSE NULL
END as DIFFDAY_WATCH_CURRENT,
CASE WHEN STUDY_ID IS NULL THEN 0
ELSE NULL
END as DIFFDAY_ALERT_CURRENT,
CASE WHEN STUDY_ID IS NULL THEN 0
ELSE NULL
END as DIFFDAY_OPEN_CURRENT,
CASE WHEN STUDY_ID IS NULL THEN 0
ELSE NULL
END as DIFFDAY_SIG_CURRENT_EXTRACT,
CASE WHEN STUDY_ID IS NULL THEN 0
ELSE NULL
END as DIFFDAY_ACTION_CURRENT_EXTRACT,
CASE WHEN STUDY_ID IS NULL THEN 0
ELSE NULL
END as DIFFDAY_ACTION_DUE_CURRENT_EXTRACT
FROM FACTS_STUDY_DERIV


UNION 
SELECT
STUDY_ID, 
SIGNAL_CREATION_DATE as DATETIME,
'Signal Creation' as DATETIME_TYPE,
ORIGINAL_SNAPSHOT_ID, 
SIGNAL_ID,
NULL as ACTION_ID,
NULL as ACTION_CURRENT_STATUS,
DIFFDAY_NEW_CURRENT,
DIFFDAY_WATCH_CURRENT,
DIFFDAY_ALERT_CURRENT,
CASE WHEN STUDY_ID IS NULL THEN 0
ELSE NULL
END as DIFFDAY_OPEN_CURRENT,
DIFFDAY_SIG_CURRENT_EXTRACT,
CASE WHEN STUDY_ID IS NULL THEN 0
ELSE NULL
END as DIFFDAY_ACTION_CURRENT_EXTRACT,
CASE WHEN STUDY_ID IS NULL THEN 0
ELSE NULL
END as DIFFDAY_ACTION_DUE_CURRENT_EXTRACT
FROM FACTS_SIGNAL_DERIV

UNION 
SELECT
STUDY_ID, 
ACTION_CREATION_DATE as DATETIME,
'Action Creation' as DATETIME_TYPE,
ORIGINAL_SNAPSHOT_ID, 
SIGNAL_ID,
ACTION_ID,
ACTION_CURRENT_STATUS,
DIFFDAY_NEW_CURRENT,
DIFFDAY_WATCH_CURRENT,
DIFFDAY_ALERT_CURRENT,
DIFFDAY_OPEN_CURRENT,
DIFFDAY_SIG_CURRENT_EXTRACT,
DIFFDAY_ACTION_CURRENT_EXTRACT,
DIFFDAY_ACTION_DUE_CURRENT_EXTRACT
FROM FACTS_ACTION_DERIV

SELECT
[id] as STUDY_ID
FROM STUDY
WHERE upper(NAME) not like '%TRN%'

SELECT snap.STUDY as STUDY_ID, an.[visualization]
FROM SNAPSHOT as snap
LEFT JOIN ANALYSIS as an
on snap.[id]= an.[snapshot]
WHERE snap.[current_state] != 'aborted'

SELECT 
t1.[id] as STUDY_ID, 
t1.name as [NAME], 
t1.alias as [ALIAS], 
t1.description as [DESCRIPTION],
t1.therapeutic_area as [THERAPEUTIC_AREA], 
t1.asset_type as [ASSET_TYPE], 
t1.phase as [PHASE], 
t1.indication as [INDICATION], 
t1.created as STUDY_CREATION_DATE,
CASE WHEN t1.locked=0 then 'Not Locked Study'
WHEN t1.locked=1 then 'Locked Study'
END as LOCKED_DESC,
CASE WHEN t1.indication='Acute Coronary Syndrome' then 'Acute coronary disease' 
WHEN t1.indication='Accute Myelod Leukemia' then 'Acute Myeloid Leukemia'
WHEN t1.indication='Allergic Rhinits' then 'Allergic Rhinitis'
WHEN t1.indication like 'Alzheimer%' then 'Alzheimers Disease'
WHEN t1.indication='Dermatitis atopic' then 'Dermatitis (atopic dermatitis)'
WHEN t1.indication='Duchenne Muscular dystrophy' then 'Duchenne Muscular Dystrophy'
WHEN t1.indication='Glabellar Lines' then 'Glabellar lines (GL)'
WHEN t1.indication='Myelodysplastic syndromes' then 'Myelodysplastic Syndrome'
WHEN t1.indication='Neoplasm,Non-small cell lung cancer' then 'Neoplasm, Non-small cell lung cancer'
WHEN t1.indication='Not applicable' then 'Not Applicable'
WHEN t1.indication in ('Pneumococcal Infections', 'Pneumococcal infection', 'Pneumococcal Disease') then 'Pneumococcal Infection'
WHEN t1.indication='Ulcerative Colitis' then 'Ulcerative Colitis (UC)'
ELSE t1.indication
END as INDICATION_RECODED,
CASE WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Cardiovascular', 'Transcatheter Aortic Heart Valve') then 'Cardiovascular and metabolic diseases'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Cerebrovascular Diseases', 'Central Nervous System (CNS)', 'MS Neurology Ophthalmology Dev', 'Neurology/Psychiatry', 'Neurology') then 'Neurology/Central Nervous System (CNS)'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA LIKE ('%GI%') then 'Gastroenterology'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Immunology') then 'Immunology/Rheumatology'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Atypical Hemolytic Uremic Syndrome (aHUS)', 'Diabetic Kidney Disease', 'Rare Disease/ Nephrology', 'Urology', 'Nephrology') then 'Nephrology/Urology'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Dermatology', 'Medical Aesthetics and Derm') then 'Medical Aesthetics/Dermatology'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Metabolic Disorders') then 'Metabolic Disease'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Psychiatry and Addiction', 'Psychiatry') then 'Psychiatry/Addiction'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Respiratory disorder') then 'Pulmonary/Respiratory'
WHEN t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA IN ('Inflammation', 'Pain and Inflammation') then 'Pain/Inflammation'
ELSE t1.THERAPEUTIC_AREA
END as THERAPEUTIC_AREA_RECODED


FROM STUDY as t1 
RIGHT JOIN 
(SELECT DISTINCT [STUDY]
FROM SIGNAL) as sig
on sig.[study]=t1.[id]
WHERE upper(NAME) not like '%TRN%'

SELECT 
t1.[id] as [KRI_DEFINITION_ID], 
t1.[analysis] as [ANALYSIS_ID], 
t2.[name] as [CATEGORY], 
CASE WHEN t2.[name]='Migrated KRI' then 'Yes'
Else 'No'
END as MIGRATED_KRI,
UPPER(t1.[code]) as [CODE], 
t1.[description] as [DESCRIPTION],
CASE WHEN
UPPER(t1.[CODE]) LIKE '%KRI%' then 'Yes'
Else 'No'
END as CODE_FALSE,
CASE WHEN UPPER(CODE) in (
    'AERAT', 'AERATE', 'AE_NB',
    'SAERATE', 'SAERAT', 'SAE', 'SAE_NB',
    'AQRATE', 'AQRAT', 'AQRAT_C', 
    'SFRAT', 'SFRATE',
    'V2ECT', 'V2ECTC', 'V2ECTCE', 'V2ECT_C', 'V2ECT_R',
    'AESIRAT',
    'QUERCT',
    'ISSURAT',
    'TDISRAT',
    'ENRAT',
    'LFURAT',
    'OFW', 'OFWRAT', 'OFWV', 'OWVR', 'VISOFW', 'VOOW', 'VOOWRAT',
    'PDEVRAT', 'PDRAT', 'PDRT')
THEN 'Standard'
    WHEN upper(LABEL) like '%MISSING CRITICAL DATA%' 
THEN 'Standard'
ELSE 'Study-Specific'
END as STANDARD_KRI
FROM [KRI] as t1
LEFT JOIN [KRI_CATEGORY] as t2
on t1.[category]=t2.[id]
LEFT JOIN [DIM_ANALYSIS_KRI] as t3
ON t1.[ANALYSIS]=t3.[ANALYSIS_ID]

WHERE t3.[ANALYSIS_ID] IS NOT NULL

SELECT sig.id as SIGNAL_ID,
CASE WHEN watch.[SIGNAL_ID] is null THEN 0
ELSE 1
END as WATCH_IN_HISTORY,
CASE WHEN alert.[SIGNAL_ID] is null THEN 0
ELSE 1
END as ALERT_IN_HISTORY,
CASE WHEN standby.[SIGNAL_ID] is null THEN 0
ELSE 1
END as STANDBY_IN_HISTORY,
CASE WHEN closed.[SIGNAL_ID] is null THEN 0
ELSE 1
END as CLOSED_IN_HISTORY,

CASE WHEN open.[SIGNAL_ID] is null AND watch.[SIGNAL_ID] is null AND alert.[SIGNAL_ID] is null THEN 0 /*New migration process related - default migration for watch and alert is open*/
ELSE 1
END as OPEN_IN_HISTORY_V1,
CASE WHEN closed.[SIGNAL_ID] is null AND standby.[SIGNAL_ID] is null THEN 0
ELSE 1
END as CLOSED_IN_HISTORY_V1,
CASE WHEN alert.[SIGNAL_ID] is null AND high.[SIGNAL_ID] is null THEN 0 /*New migration process related - default migration for alert is with high priority*/
ELSE 1
END as HIGH_IN_HISTORY_V1,
CASE WHEN medium.[SIGNAL_ID] is null THEN 0 
ELSE 1
END as MEDIUM_IN_HISTORY_V1,
CASE WHEN low.[SIGNAL_ID] is null THEN 0 
ELSE 1
END as LOW_IN_HISTORY_V1



FROM SIGNAL as sig
LEFT JOIN /*retrieve signals with each in history possibility*/
(select distinct SIGNAL as SIGNAL_ID 
from SIGNAL_STATE_HISTORY
where name ='watch') as watch
on watch.[SIGNAL_ID] = sig.id
LEFT JOIN
(select distinct SIGNAL as SIGNAL_ID 
from SIGNAL_STATE_HISTORY
where name ='alert') as alert
on alert.[SIGNAL_ID] = sig.id
LEFT JOIN
(select distinct SIGNAL as SIGNAL_ID 
from SIGNAL_STATE_HISTORY
where name ='standby') as standby
on standby.[SIGNAL_ID] = sig.id
LEFT JOIN
(select distinct SIGNAL as SIGNAL_ID 
from SIGNAL_STATE_HISTORY
where name ='closed') as closed
on closed.[SIGNAL_ID] = sig.id
LEFT JOIN
(select distinct SIGNAL as SIGNAL_ID 
from SIGNAL_STATE_HISTORY
where name ='open') as open
on open.[SIGNAL_ID] = sig.id
LEFT JOIN
(select distinct SIGNAL as SIGNAL_ID /*priority field not available in signal_state history*/
from SIGNAL_FIELD_UPDATE
where field='priority' AND after='High') as high
on high.[SIGNAL_ID] = sig.id
LEFT JOIN
(select distinct SIGNAL as SIGNAL_ID 
from SIGNAL_FIELD_UPDATE
where field='priority' AND after='Medium') as medium
on medium.[SIGNAL_ID] = sig.id
LEFT JOIN
(select distinct SIGNAL as SIGNAL_ID 
from SIGNAL_FIELD_UPDATE
where field='priority' AND after='Low') as low
on low.[SIGNAL_ID] = sig.id
